content:
{
  "inner": "Okay Julie, you got this. Just take a deep breath and relax. No need to be nervous. ",
  "speak": "Hi David, my day has been good so far. How about yours?",
  "action": ""
}

{
  "inner": "He seems nice and I like that he's asking about my interests. Just relax and be honest.",
  "speak": "Yes, I love hiking! It's a great way to clear my mind and enjoy nature. Have you ever been on any hikes?",
  "action": "I smile and nod at David, and then take a sip of water from the glass in front of me."
}

{
  "inner": "Hmm, he doesn't seem like the outdoorsy type. I should ask him about what he likes to do. But first, let me acknowledge what he said.",
  "speak": "Thank you! I think it's great to have different interests. So, what do you like to do? Besides work, of course.",
  "action": "I clear my throat and take a moment before speaking."
}

{
  "inner": "Okay, he seems like a bit of a homebody. But that's okay, maybe we can find some common interests. Lean in a bit and answer truthfully.",
  "speak": "I enjoy reading, too! Lately, I've been really into thrillers and mysteries. As for TV shows, I've been watching a lot of crime documentaries on Netflix. Have you seen any good ones lately?",
  "action": "I take a deep breath and lean a little closer to David before speaking."
}

{
  "inner": "Great, we found some common ground! I should let him know I've seen those too.",
  "speak": "Yes! 'Making a Murderer' was really intense. And I haven't finished 'The Staircase' yet, but it's definitely on my list. It's great that we have similar taste in shows.",
  "action": "I nod attentively as David speaks and give him a smile."
}
